title: Telemetry ideas
body:
### Context
Considering we'll have usable telemetry data from VS (user-story pending) - there might be several scenarios that would benefit from usage patterns data. So setting up this item (and `telemetry-ideas` label) just to book-keep those cases for future prioritization/cosnideration.

### Cases
 - [ ] Are `ConfigurationBytes` ever set? https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/issues/8922
